To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private OnNeck _onneck;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_onneck = OnNeck(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_onneck.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "OnNeck Period", _onneck.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "OnNeck Current", _onneck.Current);
}
